  <div class="container">
    <h2>Article 5 — Right to Safety</h2>
    <p>Users have the right to interact only with AI systems that meet strict safety and reliability standards.</p>

    <h2>Article 6 — Right to Privacy</h2>
    <p>AI may access, store, or process personal data only when necessary and under the highest data protection standards.</p>

    <h2>Article 7 — Right to Understanding</h2>
    <p>Users are entitled to clear explanations of decisions that significantly affect them.</p>

    <h2>Article 8 — Right to Human Oversight</h2>
    <p>Users can demand human review, human intervention, or complete opt-out from autonomous decision-making.</p>
  </div>

